File description
NB_AG_121.txt: Microarray dataset (10042 by 498, normalized data)
NB_NGS_121.txt: RNA-seq dataset (10042 by 498, normalized data)
NBT_1ma_1ngs.txt: the mapping between 10042 microarray probes and RNA-seq reads
